data.description: This beautiful one-story home has a covered front porch with built-in wiring for a ceiling fan and an open space concept with hardwire built into the home for a surround sound speaker system. Plantation Shutters throughout the whole house. 19' x 20' GARAGE: 2-car garage w/ epoxy flooring, built-in cabinets, and 2 ceiling-mounted storage racks. The laundry room has upgraded cabinets, w/ a deep stainless steel sink. The kitchen has a spacious walk-in pantry with plenty of cabinet space. Moen water-sense kitchen faucet with the sink can be turned on and off with the wave of a hand. Glass tile back-splash in the kitchen covers the wall under the cabinets. Silestone-counter tops in the Kitchen and bathrooms and laundry room. The backyard covered patio is pre-wired for a ceiling fan.
